Tests Done by Hand:
Sean:
    -Create Chatroom:
        Input Unique Name with valid users: Successfully creates.
        Input Non-Unique Name with valid users: Returns to create_chat with error message.
        Input Unique Name with non-valid users: Adds every valid user, ignores non-valid
        Input Non-Unique Name with non-valid users: Returns to create_chat with error message.

    -Leave Chatroom:
        When "No" selected: returns to show all chatrooms, user stays in room.
        When "Yes" selected: Removes current user, returns to show all chatrooms.

    -Invite to Chatroom:
        Input valid names: Successfully adds valid users.
        Input non-valid names: Ignores non-valid names, adds valid ones
